    <title>Combined summary - BIP Proposal: Compact Client Side Filtering for Light Clients</title>
    <updated>2025-09-26T15:50:18.922732+00:00</updated>
    <link href="https://gnusha.org/url/https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2017-June/014474.html" rel="alternate"/>
